\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl360
\ls3\ilvl0
\f0\fs32 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}So there are some assumptions that I felt compelled to make to answer certain questions about this collection before setting off\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sl360
\ls3\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}The collection was brought together by an individual, not a corporation\
{\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}The deed of gift has been signed and no tax receipt was requested\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sl360
\ls3\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}Both of these are significant when we arrange archival collections\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sl360
\ls3\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}All materials were created by individuals who have been dead for 50 years\
{\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}The copyright term on corporate materials has lapsed\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sl360
\ls3\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}Both of these are significant for copyright reasons - basically, the material is in the public domain\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sl360
\ls3\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}No donor restrictions were placed on the materials\
{\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}Nothing has been identified as a privacy concern during \'a0appraisal/arrangement\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\sl360
\ls3\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}Both of these are significant for access reasons\
\pard\pardeftab720

