\ls18\ilvl0
\f0\fs32 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}Finally, we establish mechanisms to add value to our collection - and to the library as a whole - by committing to ongoing outreach initiatives\
{\listtext	\'95	}We can pollinate the catalogue with links to digital content so that people searching through the catalogue can access the digital object\
{\listtext	\'95	}It\'92s also really important to find new ways to connect to community partners \
{\listtext	\'95	}For example, we might:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sl360
\ls18\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}Creating a recipe collection where we tag not only dish titles but ingredients and cooking methods\
{\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}Social tagging is a great way to flush out metadata especially with regard to individuals and places, which the archivist and cataloguer might not know\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sl360
\ls18\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}Depending on dates, I could see a place like Black Creek Pioneer Village or a genealogical group being very interested in using the materials for exhibitions or teaching tools\
